  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2571670/extras/1a57e6ef3990f853f2271f6633e4e834.avif?t=1774442335\" width=600 height=84 /></span><br>Buy tables and shelves. Fill shelves with beverages like beer or whisky. Hire waitresses and other workers to help you make your customers happy.<br>Remember - happy customers are paying customers!<br>But also keep an eye on your workers happiness, otherwise they might leave you!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2571670/extras/7ce7731622a1cf80ba75bef6194a4d7f.avif?t=1774442335\" width=600 height=84 /></span><br>Besides all of your customers being thirsty some customers enter also your saloon hungry. Build a kitchen and cook them some food.<br>Serving food pays better but requires more work. You can also hire chefs to help you!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2571670/extras/d39ca794980ee4ca8fef08a47f89f39d.avif?t=1774442335\" width=600 height=84 /></span><br>You can place objects and decorations freely in your saloon. Choose between multiple objects to place, like tables, shelves, bars, furnaces and more!",
